---
title: Greek-Style Chicken & Haloumi Gyros with Fries, Cucumber Tzatziki & Pickled Onion
description: Savour the vibrant flavors of Greek street food with tender, marinated chicken and grilled haloumi nestled in a warm torttilla alongside crispy fries, cool cucumber tzatziki, and tangy pickled onions. Each bite is a delightful dance of textures and tastes, transporting you straight to a sun-drenched Mediterranean market!
